## 7. Backend AI Route (server/routes/ai.js) - General Flow

**Note:** The `ai.js` route handles text-based tools and doesn't have special handling for imageOnly tools. The `imageOnly` property is a frontend-only control that:
1. Skips the AI text streaming endpoint entirely
2. Instead calls the dedicated `/api/image/generate-logo` endpoint
3. Provides a different UI experience

The AI route (lines 26-153) handles standard tool generation with:
- Plan-based access control (free, grow, scale, evolution, admin)
- Anthropic API streaming (claude-sonnet-4-6)
- Language localization support
- Rate limiting (60 requests per 15 minutes)

